{"word":"δείελος","slug":"δείελος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δείελος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δείλη'><el>δείλη</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>of</i> or <i>belonging to evening</i>, <el>δείελον ἦμαρ</el> <i>eventide</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a> (<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>χρόνος</el>), <i>late evening</i>, <el>εἰσόκεν ἔλθηι δείελος</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}